name: My Window #18
description:
Sometimes my shadow comes to me
It carries me to my deepest fears
Making me think and overthink
I am my oldest fears
They carry me over my quotidian thinking that I may never solve my fear

FUCK! I love minting
This is like a secret, I really don't know if somebody read descriptions.

Sometimes writing here is leaving something 
that since now does not belong to me anymore.
